entation\",\n      \"reason\": \"Spring Boot's normal auto-configuration test pattern for this module uses ApplicationContextRunner to verify bean creation and conditional back-off behavior.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No Docker image, external service, API key, or environment variable is needed. Prefer an in-process Spring Boot auto-configuration test that verifies the default context creates ChatMemoryRepository and ChatMemory beans, backs off when user beans are supplied, and exercises basic in-memory chat-memory operations.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Because the target POM marks its Spring AI model and Spring Boot dependencies optional, a scaffold that only depends on the target artifact may fail to compile or load the auto-configuration class.\",\n    \"Local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative for whether Spring Boot 4.1.0-RC1 test dependencies resolve cleanly in the harness.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01a3bc29ede5419d016a3f4a0df5248190b194be990137891a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1279, "output": 943, "cacheRead": 24064, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26286, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782532613220, "responseId": "resp_01a3bc29ede5419d016a3f4a05aa1c81908107a43dc6342686"}, "toolResults": []}
